Even if I want to help you refuse,

57
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:29,680
she won't listen to me.

58
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:31,600
Aunt.

59
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:33,600
Could it be that I truly have no choice

60
00:03:33,600 --> 00:03:35,200
but to be manipulated by her?

61
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:36,720
In a few days,

62
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:38,640
the Xiqi delegation will arrive,

63
00:03:38,640 --> 00:03:40,840
and there will be no turning back.

64
00:03:41,600 --> 00:03:42,640
Li's position

65
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:44,000
is not yet secure.

66
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,600
The marriage alliance

67
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:47,280
is for border stability.

68
00:03:47,920 --> 00:03:49,960
The young master of Xiqi
is a brilliant talent

69
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:51,280
