89
00:04:58,320 --> 00:05:01,040
Slicing you into a thousand pieces
would not be too cruel.

90
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,160
I want to see

91
00:05:02,320 --> 00:05:03,800
how she'll save you this time.

92
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:04,730
For Her Majesty,

93
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:06,360
I am willing to do anything.

94
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:07,800
When we get to my palace,

95
00:05:08,080 --> 00:05:09,040
you'd better still be

96
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:10,330
as defiant as you are now.

