120
00:06:05,640 --> 00:06:07,160
and then had me brought here.

121
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:08,000
What?

122
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:10,120
You just insisted

123
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:11,720
