142
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:07,720
Feng Li!

143
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,480
Your Majesty.

144
00:07:16,200 --> 00:07:17,000
Your Majesty.

145
00:07:18,320 --> 00:07:19,120
Your Majesty!

146
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:22,970
Why is it you?

147
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:24,600
Where is Her Majesty?

148
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:26,930
Don't tell me

149
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,620
you expect Her Majesty

150
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:29,840
to serve you herself.

151
00:07:30,520 --> 00:07:31,850
Who do you think you are?

152
00:07:32,159 --> 00:07:33,840
How dare you treat me
with such disrespect?

153
00:07:33,840 --> 00:07:34,720
Let me tell you,

154
00:07:35,200 --> 00:07:37,400
I'm now Her Majesty's favorite person.

155
00:07:39,280 --> 00:07:40,080
Your Majesty.

156
00:07:41,080 --> 00:07:43,960
Her Majesty ordered me to serve you,

157
00:07:44,280 --> 00:07:45,800
her precious slave.

158
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:49,800
It depends on your performance.

159
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:51,480
If you serve me well,

160
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:53,480
I'll naturally put in

161
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:56,240
a good word for you with Her Majesty.

162
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:58,320
What are you standing there for?

163
00:07:58,320 --> 00:07:59,400
Get me some water.

164
00:07:59,400 --> 00:08:01,460
Are you trying to let me die of thirst?

165
00:08:10,400 --> 00:08:11,520
Where's my water?

166
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:21,400
How dare you! What are you doing?

167
00:08:21,960 --> 00:08:23,760
I'll report this to Her Majesty!

168
00:08:24,440 --> 00:08:25,400
So thirsty?

169
00:08:25,760 --> 00:08:26,320
Right.

170
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:28,280
Her Majesty specifically instructed me

171
00:08:28,280 --> 00:08:29,680
to take good care of you.

172
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:30,640
So I'll

173
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:32,640
feed you the water myself.

174
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:38,240
You...

175
00:08:39,039 --> 00:08:39,840
No!

176
00:08:40,880 --> 00:08:41,640
Help!

177
00:08:43,120 --> 00:08:44,280
Let me go!

178
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:28,880
Today's tribute tea has pine fragrance.

179
00:09:28,880 --> 00:09:31,010
Would you like to try it, Your Majesty?

180
00:09:31,560 --> 00:09:33,090
What happened to your hand?

181
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,040
The other day,

182
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:40,250
