a jade seal for Your Majesty myself.

183
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:42,040
The carving knife was sharp.

184
00:09:42,040 --> 00:09:44,040
I was careless and cut myself.

185
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:56,200
Does it hurt?

186
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,290
It doesn't hurt.

187
00:09:59,800 --> 00:10:01,000
It's already healed.

188
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:04,000
You're always like this.

189
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:07,000
You get injured

190
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,780
and never tell me about it.

191
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:12,000
That day,

192
00:10:12,560 --> 00:10:14,400
I was a bit harsh with you.

193
00:10:15,520 --> 00:10:17,050
Are you still upset with me?

194
00:10:17,760 --> 00:10:19,200
How could I be upset with you?

195
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:20,600
I was overly concerned.

196
00:10:21,560 --> 00:10:23,490
There must be some special reason.

197
00:10:23,560 --> 00:10:26,160
I should have trusted
Your Majesty's resolve.

198
00:10:31,720 --> 00:10:33,580
You're always so understanding.

199
00:10:44,640 --> 00:10:47,170
Actually, he resembles
someone from my past.

200
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:03,880
Is...

201
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:06,680
Is he the boy you once mentioned

202
00:11:06,680 --> 00:11:07,560
who was with you in the wasteland

203
00:11:07,560 --> 00:11:09,360
and survived together with you?

204
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,040
Yes.

205
00:11:12,680 --> 00:11:13,880
Fate is full of irony.

206
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:17,500
I never expected to meet
him again in the palace.

207
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:20,370
Then, Your Majesty,

208
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:23,370
